release_note: Added more Christmas backgrounds and stickers. Various bug fixes
Various bug fixes
Holiday themed backgrounds Holiday themed stickers Link for a text box. It can be a link to a web page or an internal page. Various bug fixes and improvements.

Increased sticker support Text stickers such as months days of the week encouraging quotes etc. Shape stickers in eight color schemes. You can also write on them. Many more stickers with adorable figures. Decorate pages with high quality paper texture or beautiful images. Decorate pages with pastel or neutral colors. You can combine them with background images. You can also change the foreground color of the pages. You can now choose between styles with wiring and padding for relevant elements. Various bug fixes and UI improvements.

User can copy paste duplicate text boxes. Various bug fixes If users have iCloud sync enabled in AJournal and are on the latest version of iOS make sure all devices have the same version of iOS to fully use the new drawing tools.

After selecting the drawing with the lasso tool press the new resize button to rotate it and resize it. A new compact monthly item that supports navigation by day and week. A new yearly item that supports navigation by day and week. New system templates using the compact monthly and yearly element. Set the start day of the week which will be used in various functions in AJournal. Various bugs fixed.

You can now add or edit a calendar event in AJournal directly. In the weekly calendar you can now navigate directly to a specific date by tapping on the date. In the monthly calendar you can now navigate directly to a specific week by tapping the left edge of the week or jump to a specific date by tapping the date. You can now use custom fonts in AJournal. Calendar and various UI fixes Bug fix

Getting closer You can now zoom up to 6 times in AJournal. It will be useful when handwriting small text. Easier image text selection You can now select an image or text by simply touching it without first pressing the image text buttons. Touch the outside area to deselect it. Monthly calendar integrated with the user s calendar The monthly calendar template will now display the user s calendar data. If you do not want calendar data to be displayed in the monthly calendar template create a user template and configure the monthly calendar item manually. Suggestions and ideas If you have any suggestions or ideas for improvement please share them with us using the Contact Us feature or visit our support portal via FAQ . If you like AJournal app please rate or review the app. It will be very useful for this new application. Thanks for your support!
